title: Kraftwerk Vs Pete Shelley - Witness The Mix 1995
description: yay. this is a little mix i knocked up on my 4 track porta-studio back in 95. it&#039;s kraftwerk&#039;s trans europe express attacked by pete shelley&#039;s witness the change instrumental mix. together they make a lovely couple.lol the pete shelley portion of the mix has been double tracked and phase shifts occur all over the place. but if i do say so myself, it makes the original sound dull. Slap your headphones on for this. enjoy. alan
